{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1409/comments/4928649.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:5bc443f9afa2..529c73396b21?path=gazebo%2Fgui%2FGLWidget.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1409/_/diff#comment-4928649"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1409, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1409.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1409"}}, "title": "Select a link with the mouse if parent model already selected"}, "content": {"raw": "Is there a big difference between using `==` vs. using a bitwise and `&`?\n~~~\nbool rightButton = (this->mouseEvent.button & common::MouseEvent::RIGHT);\n~~~\nSo this is checking to see that only the right mouse button is pressed? That's probably right, but I'm just checking.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Is there a big difference between using <code>==</code> vs. using a bitwise and <code>&amp;</code>?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">bool</span> <span class=\"nt\">rightButton</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">mouseEvent</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nc\">button</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"nt\">common</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">MouseEvent</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">RIGHT</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>So this is checking to see that only the right mouse button is pressed? That's probably right, but I'm just checking.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-02-02T23:24:35.993254+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": 703, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/gui/GLWidget.cc"}, "updated_on": "2015-02-02T23:24:36.003150+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 4928649}